# Changes

## [0.1.6] 2022-03-17

- Add createSelector implementation 
- Moved memoize implementation to utilities library
- Rename createAction to createActionDispatcher
- Fixed Circular dependency issue

## [0.1.7] 2022-03-21

- Fixed bug with incorrect type definitions path
- Using memoize function from functional package instead of utilities

## [0.1.9] 2022-03-30

- Add local state management `useRxState() and useRxReducer()` functions inspired by react hooks

## [0.1.10] 2022-03-31

- Add useRxEffect function for running side effects
- Rename Dispatch to useDispatch
- Fixed bug in old Dispatch method implementation
- Bug fix in Store decorator

## [0.1.12] 2022-03-31

- Moved useRxEffect, useRxReducer and useRxState into a dedicated package